org.apache.iceberg.spark.actions

Class SparkActions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.iceberg.spark.actions.SparkActions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionsProvider

    public class SparkActions
extends java.lang.Object
implements ActionsProvider
    An implementation of ActionsProvider for Spark.

    This class is the primary API for interacting with actions in Spark that users should use to instantiate particular actions.
